Ambanc to open second Terre Haute office . Ambanc Indiana , a unit of Ambanc Corp , said Tuesday it will build a second branch banking office in Terre Haute , Indiana , that is expected to open for business in the first quarter of 1998 . Ambanc Indiana officials said the economic climate in the area and the potential for growth warrants opening the new facility , which will be added to a roster of 15 branches currently operating in five Indiana counties . Ambanc is a bank holding company with assets of more than $ 725 million and 25 banking offices in southwest Indiana and southeast Illinois . ( ( Chicago newsdesk ( 312 ) 408 - 8787 ) ) 
